title: "ExeFoundry: BAT to EXE Converter (portable)"
type: software
abstract: >
  ExeFoundry is a single-file Windows tool that compiles Batch (.bat) scripts
  into portable .exe files using the built-in C# compiler (csc). It supports
  custom icons, console/GUI mode, and argument forwarding. Open source (MIT).

